Package: Texevier
Type: Package
Title: Texevier: Create Formal written documents with the Elsevier format using R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nico", "Katzke", email = "nfkatzke@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
ctb: Nicolaas Odendaal
Maintainer: Nico Katzke <nfkatzke@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    rmarkdown,
    knitr,
    xtable,
    ggthemes,
	readr
Suggests:
	xts
Description: This package provides users with a quick means of setting up
    the standard accepted academic paper layout in the Elsevier format. Users will have to have
    Latex installed first, as well as the latest rmarkdown version and Rstudio. This package
	creates an easily useable template for doing formal write-ups in the Elsevier format.
